00:00:18.584 --> 00:00:22.114
So they tell us its speed
is inversely proportional,

00:00:22.114 --> 00:00:22.947
to what?

00:00:22.947 --> 00:00:26.805
To the square of the
distance, S, it has traveled.

00:00:26.805 --> 00:00:27.979
So S

00:00:27.979 --> 00:00:29.729
is equal to distance.

