I wrote a proportionality constant,

00:01:08.403 --> 00:01:09.236
over what?

00:01:09.236 --> 00:01:11.320
It's inversely proportional to what?

00:01:11.320 --> 00:01:13.349
To the square of the distance!

00:01:13.349 --> 00:01:16.410
To the square of the
distance it has traveled.

00:01:16.410 --> 00:01:17.243
